  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 7fe549ab24e47ae42a47e0e5aa9ae7b8, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NotebookManager
  bookPanel: {fileID: 1776568575}
  leftPageText: {fileID: 8292145}
  rightPageText: {fileID: 0}
  pageNumberText: {fileID: 563397876}
  nextButton: {fileID: 1862359164}
  prevButton: {fileID: 1642595445}
  singleNotePanel: {fileID: 0}
  singleNoteText: {fileID: 0}
  defaultStartingPage: "Kendi haf\u0131zan\u0131 silmen, i\u015Fledi\u011Fin g\xFCnahlar\u0131
    temizlemiyor. \nSu\xE7u hep sisteme att\u0131n ama deney kontrolden \xE7\u0131kt\u0131\u011F\u0131nda
    bizi o odaya kilitleyen sendin."
  collectedPages:
  - "Onlar\u0131n \xE7\u0131\u011Fl\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131 dinlerken ana kap\u0131n\u0131n
    g\xFCvenlik \u015Fifresini de\u011Fi\u015Ftirdin. Kimse ka\xE7amas\u0131n, kimse
    ger\xE7e\u011Fi \xF6\u011Frenmesin diye..."
  - "E\u011Fer bu notu bulduysan ve o zavall\u0131 beynin hala hi\xE7bir \u015Fey
    hat\u0131rlam\u0131yorsa, art\u0131k son bir se\xE7imin var:"
  - "Ya o \u015Fifreyle \xE7\u0131k\u0131p bu tatl\u0131 yalanda ya\u015Famaya devam
    et, ya da di\u011Fer kap\u0131ya y\xFCr\xFC ve bize ya\u015Fatt\u0131\u011F\u0131n
    cehennemle y\xFCzle\u015F."
