  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 8bb18310da12b6a4d81128226063c8ce, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::GameEndManager
  blackPanel: {fileID: 615799660}
  narrativeText: {fileID: 919722095}
  choicePanel: {fileID: 352915173}
  heartbeatSound: {fileID: 8300000, guid: a40ed37438a9f83459d2f1301df95975, type: 3}
  slamSound: {fileID: 0}
  glitchSes: {fileID: 0}
  betrayalText: "Sonunda kap\u0131y\u0131 a\xE7t\u0131n ve elimize d\xFC\u015Ft\xFCn.\nKendi
    \xE7\u0131karlar\u0131n i\xE7in bizi hapsetti\u011Fin bu yerde sen \xE7\xFCr\xFCyeceksin."
  trueEndingIntroText: "Ger\xE7ekleri oldu\u011Fu gibi kabullenmeye haz\u0131r m\u0131s\u0131n,
    yoksa bu tatl\u0131 yalanda ya\u015Famaya devam m\u0131 edeceksin?"
  trueEndingRememberText: "O g\xFCn o kap\u0131y\u0131 \xFCzerlerine kilitledi\u011Fimde
    \xE7\u0131\u011Fl\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131 duymamazl\u0131ktan gelmi\u015Ftim.\n\u015Eimdi
    her \u015Fey \xE7ok net. \nY ve Z feda edilmeliydi. Ger\xE7ekleri \xF6\u011Frenmemeleri
    i\xE7in \xF6lmelilerdi. \nBen bir kurban de\u011Filim... \nBen hayatta kalan\u0131m.
    \nVe bunun i\xE7in hi\xE7 pi\u015Fman de\u011Filim.\nPi\u015Fman olacak veya
    unutacak de\u011Filim, onlar\u0131n korkak\xE7a hatalar\u0131n\u0131n bedelini
    ben \xF6deyemezdim. Bu deney i\xE7in \xE7ok emek verdim."
  trueEndingForgetText: "Korkak.\nSen bu d\xF6ng\xFCde kalmaya mahkumsun.\nDuvarlardaki
    her notu unutmay\u0131 se\xE7ip tekrar tekrar ba\u015Fa d\xF6nd\xFC\u011F\xFCnde
    kendin yazd\u0131n.\nYapt\u0131klar\u0131nla y\xFCzle\u015Febilene kadar bu d\xF6ng\xFCn\xFCn
    i\xE7inde kalacaks\u0131n."
